<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .proposal-title {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #0066cc;
        }
        .feedback-box {
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            border-radius: 4px;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            white-space: pre-wrap;
            word-wrap: break-word;
        }
        .signature {
            margin-top: 30px;
            font-style: italic;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <p>Dear {{object.owner.username}},</p>

    <p>Your proposal titled <span class="proposal-title">"{{object.title}}"</span> has been marked for revision.<br>
    Please review the feedback provided and resubmit your proposal when ready.</p>

    <p>See the internal comments for details on what needs to be revised:</p>

    <div class="feedback-box">{{ object.internal_notes }}</div>

    <p class="signature">Best regards,<br>
    The ZAM Program Review Team</p>
</body>
</html>

